entities.createSql: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`farm_id` TEXT NOT NULL, `name` TEXT, PRIMARY KEY(`farm_id`))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`intervention_id` INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `intervention_id_eky` INTEGER, `type` TEXT, `output` INTEGER, `water_quantity` INTEGER, `water_unit` TEXT, `farm` TEXT, `comment` TEXT, `status` TEXT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`wd_id` INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `wd_intervention_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `hour_duration` INTEGER NOT NULL, `execution_date` TEXT NOT NULL, FOREIGN KEY(`wd_intervention_id`) REFERENCES `interventions`(`intervention_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE CASCADE )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`phyto_id` INTEGER, `phyto_id_eky` INTEGER, `name` TEXT, `nature` TEXT, `maaid` TEXT, `mix_category_code` INTEGER, `in_field_reentry_delay` INTEGER, `firm_name` TEXT, `registered` INTEGER, `used` INTEGER, `unit` TEXT, PRIMARY KEY(`phyto_id`))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`quantity` REAL NOT NULL, `unit` TEXT, `intervention_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `phytosanitary_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`intervention_id`, `phytosanitary_id`), FOREIGN KEY(`intervention_id`) REFERENCES `interventions`(`intervention_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE CASCADE , FOREIGN KEY(`phytosanitary_id`) REFERENCES `phytos`(`phyto_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION )
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`product_id` INTEGER, `dose` REAL, PRIMARY KEY(`product_id`))
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`seed_id` INTEGER, `seed_id_eky` INTEGER, `specie` TEXT, `variety` TEXT, `registered` INTEGER, `used` INTEGER, `unit` TEXT, PRIMARY KEY(`seed_id`))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`quantity` REAL NOT NULL, `unit` TEXT, `intervention_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `seed_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`intervention_id`, `seed_id`), FOREIGN KEY(`intervention_id`) REFERENCES `interventions`(`intervention_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE CASCADE , FOREIGN KEY(`seed_id`) REFERENCES `seeds`(`seed_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`fertilizer_id` INTEGER, `fertilizer_id_eky` INTEGER, `name` TEXT, `label_fra` TEXT, `variant` TEXT, `variety` TEXT, `derivative_of` TEXT, `nature` TEXT, `nitrogen_concentration` TEXT, `phosphorus_concentration` TEXT, `potassium_concentration` TEXT, `sulfur_trioxyde_concentration` TEXT, `registered` INTEGER, `used` INTEGER, `unit` TEXT, PRIMARY KEY(`fertilizer_id`))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`quantity` REAL NOT NULL, `unit` TEXT, `intervention_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `fertilizer_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`intervention_id`, `fertilizer_id`), FOREIGN KEY(`intervention_id`) REFERENCES `interventions`(`intervention_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE CASCADE , FOREIGN KEY(`fertilizer_id`) REFERENCES `fertilizers`(`fertilizer_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION )
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`material_id` INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `name` TEXT, `description` TEXT, `unit` TEXT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`quantity` INTEGER, `unit` TEXT, `approximative_value` INTEGER, `intervention_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `material_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`intervention_id`, `material_id`), FOREIGN KEY(`intervention_id`) REFERENCES `interventions`(`intervention_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE CASCADE , FOREIGN KEY(`material_id`) REFERENCES `materials`(`material_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION )
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`equipment_id` INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `equipment_id_eky` INTEGER, `name` TEXT, `number` TEXT, `type` TEXT, `farmId` TEXT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`intervention_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `equipment_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`intervention_id`, `equipment_id`), FOREIGN KEY(`intervention_id`) REFERENCES `interventions`(`intervention_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE CASCADE , FOREIGN KEY(`equipment_id`) REFERENCES `equipments`(`equipment_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION )
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`person_id` INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, `person_id_eky` INTEGER, `first_name` TEXT, `last_name` TEXT, `role` TEXT, `farm_id` TEXT)

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`intervention_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `person_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `is_driver` INTEGER, PRIMARY KEY(`intervention_id`, `person_id`), FOREIGN KEY(`intervention_id`) REFERENCES `interventions`(`intervention_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE CASCADE , FOREIGN KEY(`person_id`) REFERENCES `persons`(`person_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`intervention_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `temperature` REAL, `wind_speed` REAL, `description` TEXT, PRIMARY KEY(`intervention_id`), FOREIGN KEY(`intervention_id`) REFERENCES `interventions`(`intervention_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE CASCADE )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`harvest_id` INTEGER, `id_intervention` INTEGER, `id_storage` INTEGER, `quantity` REAL, `unit` TEXT, `number` TEXT, `type` TEXT, PRIMARY KEY(`harvest_id`), FOREIGN KEY(`id_storage`) REFERENCES `storages`(`storage_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE CASCADE )
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`storage_id` INTEGER, `name` TEXT, `type` TEXT, PRIMARY KEY(`storage_id`))

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`crop_uuid` TEXT NOT NULL, `name` TEXT, `specie` TEXT, `production_nature` TEXT, `production_mode` TEXT, `production_output` TEXT, `provisional_yield` TEXT, `shape` TEXT, `surface_area` REAL NOT NULL, `centroid` TEXT, `start_date` TEXT, `stop_date` TEXT, `plot` TEXT, `farm` TEXT, PRIMARY KEY(`crop_uuid`), FOREIGN KEY(`plot`) REFERENCES `plots`(`plot_uuid`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`intervention_id` INTEGER NOT NULL, `crop_id_id` TEXT NOT NULL, `work_area_percentage` INTEGER, PRIMARY KEY(`intervention_id`, `crop_id_id`), FOREIGN KEY(`intervention_id`) REFERENCES `interventions`(`intervention_id`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE CASCADE , FOREIGN KEY(`crop_id_id`) REFERENCES `crops`(`crop_uuid`) ON UPDATE NO ACTION ON DELETE NO ACTION )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`plot_uuid` TEXT NOT NULL, `name` TEXT, `shape` TEXT, `surface_area` REAL NOT NULL, `centroid` TEXT, `startDate` TEXT, `stopDate` TEXT, `farm` TEXT, PRIMARY KEY(`plot_uuid`))
